Show HN: Scramble – Automatic API documentation generator for Laravel
text:
Scramble generates OpenAPI docs without requiring you to write PHPDoc annotations.

This allows you to always have up-to-date docs based on the actual codebase.

title: Ask HN: How would you build a system to get news fast?
text:
I'm doing a thought experiment and wondering how I would get news about specific companies fast. This means not leveraging RSS feeds or news aggregators. The closest commercial offering I can think of is something like Benzinga.

Given the above requirements, how would you build such a system?
